target: What time do you want to arrive by?
context: <user> Hello, I need to book a train at 07:15 leaving Cambridge going to the town center on Thursday for 7 people. <system> Sure I can help with that. There are no trains going to the town centre. Do you have another destination in mind? <user> Could you check for a bus? <system> I think we may need to recheck your intended arrival location. To where and from where do you wish to travel? <user> I am leaving from Cambridge at 14:30. <system> And where are you going? <user> I will be going to ely. <system>
